theorem interior_union_eq_of_isOpen_left {X : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X]
    {A B : Set X} (hA : IsOpen (A : Set X)) :
    interior (A ∪ B : Set X) = A ∪ interior (B : Set X) := by
  -- We prove the two inclusions separately.
  apply Set.Subset.antisymm
  · -- `interior (A ∪ B) ⊆ A ∪ interior B`
    intro x hxInt
    have hxUnion : (x : X) ∈ (A ∪ B : Set X) := interior_subset hxInt
    by_cases hAx : (x : X) ∈ A
    · exact Or.inl hAx
    · -- Since `x ∈ interior (A ∪ B)` and `x ∉ A`, we will show `x ∈ interior B`.
      rcases hxInt with ⟨U, hUopen, hxU, hU_sub⟩
      -- Consider `V = U \ A`, an open neighborhood of `x` contained in `B`.
      set V : Set X := U \ A
      have hV_open : IsOpen V := hUopen.diff hA
      have hxV : (x : X) ∈ V := by
        refine And.intro hxU ?_
        exact hAx
      have hV_sub_B : (V : Set X) ⊆ B := by
        intro y hy
        have hyU : (y : X) ∈ U := hy.1
        have hNotA : (y : X) ∉ A := hy.2
        have hyUnion : (y : X) ∈ (A ∪ B : Set X) := hU_sub hyU
        cases hyUnion with
        | inl hyA => exact (False.elim (hNotA hyA))
        | inr hyB => exact hyB
      exact Or.inr ⟨V, hV_open, hxV, hV_sub_B⟩
  · -- `A ∪ interior B ⊆ interior (A ∪ B)`
    intro x hxUnion
    -- The set `A ∪ interior B` is open.
    have hOpen : IsOpen ((A : Set X) ∪ interior (B : Set X)) :=
      hA.union isOpen_interior
    -- It is contained in `A ∪ B`.
    have hSub : (A ∪ interior (B : Set X)) ⊆ (A ∪ B : Set X) := by
      intro y hy
      cases hy with
      | inl hyA => exact Or.inl hyA
      | inr hyIntB => exact Or.inr (interior_subset hyIntB)
    -- Hence it is contained in the interior of `A ∪ B`.
    exact (interior_maximal hSub hOpen) hxUnion

theorem closure_iUnion_subset_closure {X : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X] {ι : Sort _}
    (f : ι → Set X) :
    (⋃ i, closure (f i : Set X)) ⊆ closure (⋃ i, f i : Set X) := by
  intro x hx
  rcases Set.mem_iUnion.mp hx with ⟨i, hxi⟩
  have h_mono : closure (f i : Set X) ⊆ closure (⋃ j, f j : Set X) := by
    apply closure_mono
    intro y hy
    exact Set.mem_iUnion.mpr ⟨i, hy⟩
  exact h_mono hxi
